Princess Kara (amụrụ n'afọ 2000) bụ onye Naijirịa na-atụba discus
O meriri ma National Championships na African Under 20 Championships na 2019
Ihe kacha mma ya bụ 50.07 (  3+1⁄4 in).
Kara sonyere na 2016 National Youth Games ma sọọ mpi na triple jump na shot put.

Kara ritere ọla edo na ịgba ọsọ na 2018 National Sports Festival (NSF) na Abuja. N'afọ 2019, ọ meriri ma asọmpi mba n'okpuru afọ 20 na asọmpi African Under 20, malite ịma Chinwe Okoro na Chioma Onyekwere aka maka ọnọdụ mbụ na Naijirịa. Na Under 20 African Championships (nke e mere  Abidjan), o dekọrọ ihe kachasị mma nke 50.04 m (164  in), nke meriri akara kachasị elu ya n'oge gara aga karịa mita ise. Mgbe ahụ, o setịpụrụ ihe kachasị mma nke onwe ya nke 50.07 (  3+1⁄4 in) na ule iru eru maka 2019 All Africa Games, mechara bụrụ onye nke ise n'egwuregwu ahụ  ịtụba 49.85 (  6+1⁄2 in)
O nwetakwara mmeri na 2019 National Championships.
O sonyere na Central Arizona College, ebe ọ meriri NJCAA Division I Outdoor discus titles n'usoro na 2021 na 2022.
